</svg></button><header><h1>Cookie Policy</h1></header><section><p>This Cookie Policy explains how Awarcrown Corporations LLP ("Company," "we," "us," and "our") uses cookies and similar technologies to recognize you when you visit our website at <a href=http://www.cybertron7.in>www.cybertron7.in</a> ("Website"). It explains what these technologies are, why we use them, and your rights to control their use.<p>In some cases, we may use cookies to collect personal information, or that becomes personal information if we combine it with other data.</section><section><h2>What Are Cookies?</h2><p>Cookies are small data files placed on your computer or mobile device when you visit a website. They are widely used to make websites function efficiently and provide reporting information.<p>Cookies set by the website owner (Awarcrown Corporations LLP) are called "first-party cookies." Cookies set by other parties are called "third-party cookies." Third-party cookies enable external features such as advertising, analytics, and interactive content.</section><section><h2>Why Do We Use Cookies?</h2><p>We use both first- and third-party cookies for various reasons:<ul><li><strong>Essential Cookies:</strong> Required for our Website to function properly.<li><strong>Analytics Cookies:</strong> Help us understand Website usage and improve performance.<li><strong>Advertising Cookies:</strong> Used to show relevant advertisements based on user interests.</ul></section><section><h2>How Can You Control Cookies?</h2><p>You have the right to accept or reject cookies. The Cookie Consent Manager on our Website allows you to select which categories of cookies you accept or reject. Essential cookies cannot be rejected.<p>You can also manage cookies via your browser settings:<ul><li><a href=https://support.google.com/chrome/answer/95647 target=_blank>Google Chrome</a><li><a href=https://support.mozilla.org/en-US/kb/enable-and-disable-cookies-website-preferences target=_blank>Mozilla Firefox</a><li><a href=https://support.apple.com/en-us/HT201265 target=_blank>Safari</a><li><a href=https://support.microsoft.com/en-us/microsoft-edge/microsoft-edge-browsing-data-and-privacy-bb8174ba-9d73-dcf2-9b4a-c582b4e640dd target=_blank>Microsoft Edge</a><li><a href=https://help.opera.com/en/latest/web-preferences/#cookies target=_blank>Opera</a></ul></section><section><h2>Types of Cookies We Use</h2><table><thead><tr><th>Cookie Name<th>Purpose<th>Provider<th>Type<th>Expiration<tbody><tr><td>JSESSIONID<td>Maintains anonymous user session<td>seal.godaddy.com<td>Server Cookie<td>Session<tr><td>s7<td>Tracks site usage and behavior<td>.cybertron7.in<td>HTTP Cookie<td>29 minutes<tr><td>event<td>Gathers event data<td>events.api.secureserver.net<td>Pixel Tracker<td>Session</table></section><section><h2>Other Tracking Technologies</h2><p>We may use other tracking technologies like web beacons (tracking pixels) to analyze Website traffic, improve performance, and measure marketing effectiveness. These technologies often rely on cookies.</section><section><h2>Targeted Advertising</h2><p>Third-party advertisers may use cookies to serve relevant ads. These cookies do not store personal details unless you provide them.</section><section><h2>Updates to This Policy</h2><p>We may update this Cookie Policy periodically to reflect changes in our practices. Please check this page regularly.</section><section><h2>Contact Us</h2><p>If you have any questions about our use of cookies, contact us at:<p>Awarcrown Corporations LLP<br>Tenali, Andhra Pradesh 523201, India</section></div>